data.description: SELLER IS OFFERING $10,000 IN BUYER CREDITS TOWARDS BUY DOWN POINTS OR TOWARDS CLOSING COST!!  Stunning, move in ready home built in 2015! This 4 bedroom, 2 bath, 2300 square foot home features an open concept, split floor plan, with an impressive kitchen. The kitchen is a chef's dream incorporating granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, custom cabinetry, a bar height eating area, and a breakfast nook. This home features high ceilings throughout, a dining room, wood and tile throughout the main living areas. Owners closed in additional space which provides more living space/bonus room. On one side of the home you will find: three oversized bedrooms and a full bathroom with tub. Located on the other side is a laundry room with custom cabinets and two car garage. Opposite the living area is the private primary bedroom and en suite. The primary en-suite features granite counters, dual sinks, separate soaking tub, walk-in shower, and a large walk-in closet.. The beautifully landscaped yard has expansive green space, a fully fenced in back yard and a playground.  HOA for the neighborhood covers lawn maintenance! Fairways Edge is conveniently located to Laurel Island Links, schools, shopping, restaurants, Kings Bay Naval Base, and I-95, giving you quick access to Jacksonville, Fernandina Beach and Brunswick!
